			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "goto 284.28, 1.49, 302.48\r\nTalk to ShadowHeart\r\nSelect option 3. You were kidnapped by those creatures as well?\r\nSelect option 3. Calm down. We escaped - we survived. There's no need for dramatics.\r\nSelect option 2. I doubt this is the only entrance. You could look elsewhere.\r\nSelect option 4. I'm leaving before more things crawl out of the wreckage\r\niin recon \"goto 220.91, 30.62, 407.16\"\r\nTrigger Plea at the gates\r\n in recon \"killcombat\"\r\nin recon \"goto 218.14, 25.97, 539.96\"\r\nInteract with Shadowheart"
				},
